description: If you've been swept away by the ambient jazz-flute vibes of André 3000's new album New Blue Sun, this playlist is where you need to go next, with over 2 hours of music from artists like Alice Coltrane, McCoy Tyner, Yusef Lateef, Hermeto Pascoal, and many more.
name: Jazz Dispensary's Gateway to André 3000's New Blue Sun
